Pantheon Vision Board v1

Core idea

A living board with five layers:
	1.	See — your goals, symbols, and desired future
	2.	Measure — real progress data
	3.	Interpret — AI explains what the data means
	4.	Advise — next best moves
	5.	Adapt — the board evolves as your life changes

This makes it more than motivation wallpaper. It becomes a feedback engine.

