4. Counsel panel

This is the AI advisor area.

Instead of generic coaching, it gives four kinds of readouts:

Mirror — what’s true right now
Hound — what looks off or inconsistent
Dragonfly — alternative perspective
Goblin — where leverage/value is hiding

Example:
